WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 33=

01:39.290 --> 01:40.180
Make way.

01:45.210 --> 01:46.050
Mr. Mu.

01:46.900 --> 01:47.930
Why are you here?

01:47.930 --> 01:49.210
Miss Cai,

01:49.210 --> 01:52.740
the Young Master came here to propose.

01:54.980 --> 01:55.850
Two years apart,

01:55.850 --> 01:56.770
Manager Zhao

01:56.770 --> 01:58.050
has become impressive.

01:58.050 --> 01:59.050
She brought two men back.

01:59.380 --> 02:00.330
Impressive.

02:00.330 --> 02:02.020
As expected of the manager.

02:03.930 --> 02:04.770
Mr. Mu,

02:05.210 --> 02:07.380
Zhao was just confined over you,

02:07.380 --> 02:08.783
and you came so openly.

02:08.794 --> 02:10.474
You're putting her
in an awkward position.

02:11.010 --> 02:12.500
Please, go back.

02:12.500 --> 02:14.380
Don't provoke a sect conflict.

02:14.660 --> 02:15.570
Mr. Song,

02:16.130 --> 02:17.610
I think what you just said

02:17.980 --> 02:20.260
was biased and narrow-minded.

02:20.660 --> 02:22.220
What's wrong with a man

02:22.220 --> 02:23.690
proposing to an unmarried woman

02:23.690 --> 02:26.260
openly and honorably?

02:26.780 --> 02:27.660
Besides,

02:27.660 --> 02:29.410
we came with sincerity.

02:29.410 --> 02:31.340
The Young Master is charming,

02:31.340 --> 02:32.500
handsome,

02:32.500 --> 02:34.410
wealthy, and well-mannered.

02:34.410 --> 02:35.820
He's a martial arts prodigy.

02:35.820 --> 02:36.850
Everyone,

02:36.850 --> 02:38.780
does he match Miss Cai?

02:38.780 --> 02:40.570
Perfect match.

02:44.610 --> 02:45.610
Mr. Song,

02:45.610 --> 02:46.890
are you afraid

02:46.890 --> 02:48.610
you can't beat the Young Master,

02:49.260 --> 02:50.610
so you won't let us in?

02:52.130 --> 02:53.260
Everyone, please leave.

02:58.500 --> 02:59.340
Mr. Mu,

02:59.690 --> 03:00.820
may we speak privately?

03:02.290 --> 03:03.340
What do you want?

03:04.410 --> 03:06.170
Luoying Valley
no longer has what you want.

03:06.610 --> 03:07.450
But you are here.

03:09.410 --> 03:10.660
If I hadn't come,

03:11.220 --> 03:12.133
would I soon receive

03:12.144 --> 03:13.724
your wedding invitation with Song Yuzhi?

03:18.730 --> 03:19.570
Be serious.

03:20.540 --> 03:21.380
The Guangtian matter

03:22.060 --> 03:23.290
is led by the man in black.

03:24.010 --> 03:26.500
He used corpse slaves
to frame Song Shijun,

03:27.170 --> 03:28.540
obviously reckless,

03:29.290 --> 03:30.570
planning a final strike.

03:31.220 --> 03:33.130
We must lure him out

03:33.540 --> 03:34.500
before his next move.

03:35.540 --> 03:36.380
How?

03:36.940 --> 03:38.500
They slaughtered the Chang clan

03:38.890 --> 03:40.220
for the Jade Sunflower.

03:41.220 --> 03:42.980
Later, each step

03:42.980 --> 03:44.610
was tied to it.

03:45.130 --> 03:46.290
I've spread the word

03:46.550 --> 03:47.410
that the treasure

03:47.410 --> 03:48.980
is in my father's relics.

03:49.410 --> 03:50.610
I'll use it as a betrothal gift

03:51.340 --> 03:52.260
to marry you.

03:53.890 --> 03:55.290
Guess if the man in black

03:56.500 --> 03:57.610
will check it out.

03:58.290 --> 04:00.526
If they also seek the Ziwei Method,

04:00.537 --> 04:02.223
they must know
the Night Orchid is ruined.

04:02.410 --> 04:03.610
How can you be sure

04:03.610 --> 04:05.570
they'd still care
about the Jade Sunflower?

04:06.940 --> 04:07.980
Worth a try.

04:28.100 --> 04:29.730
You're not really here to propose.

04:30.580 --> 04:31.660
Mr. Mu,

04:31.660 --> 04:33.250
why bring so many gifts?

04:33.700 --> 04:34.980
It's my first visit.

04:35.610 --> 04:36.930
I should bring meeting gifts.

04:39.780 --> 04:41.020
This Shennong Toxin

04:41.410 --> 04:42.810
is said to be the king of poisons.

04:43.140 --> 04:43.980
Only one bottle

04:44.490 --> 04:45.330
in the world.

04:46.370 --> 04:49.580
It really exists!

04:49.580 --> 04:51.020
Restrain yourself.

04:56.920 --> 04:57.770
The king of poisons.

04:57.770 --> 04:59.100
Most toxic!

05:01.490 --> 05:02.330
Lord Cai,

05:03.410 --> 05:04.250
look at this.

05:05.250 --> 05:06.170
A dragon hook.

05:06.540 --> 05:08.410
I heard you enjoy fishing

05:08.410 --> 05:09.410
in your spare time.

05:09.730 --> 05:11.410
I hope you like it.

05:11.900 --> 05:12.740
Of course.

05:14.000 --> 05:14.850
You know so much.

05:14.850 --> 05:16.100
It's fun!

05:16.580 --> 05:18.170
Flying so high!

05:18.170 --> 05:20.340
Flying high!

05:23.050 --> 05:23.890
Cai Han.

05:25.140 --> 05:25.980
Ning,

05:26.220 --> 05:28.580
can you come here often?

05:28.580 --> 05:29.930
I like you so much!

05:31.410 --> 05:32.250
Sure.

05:33.310 --> 05:34.170
It's the real...

05:34.170 --> 05:35.900
Then I'll visit often.

05:35.900 --> 05:36.900
Every visit,

05:36.900 --> 05:38.410
I'll bring lots of fun things, okay?

05:38.410 --> 05:39.410
Yes!

05:39.980 --> 05:40.820
Stop it.

05:41.540 --> 05:43.140
You came from afar.

05:43.490 --> 05:44.370
You must be exhausted.

05:45.020 --> 05:46.610
Zhao,

05:46.610 --> 05:48.490
take Mr. Mu to rest.

05:48.930 --> 05:49.770
Let's go.

05:50.610 --> 05:51.450
Hold me.

05:53.810 --> 05:54.660
Cai Han.

05:54.660 --> 05:55.610
Okay, I'll hold you.

05:56.660 --> 05:57.500
Let's go.

05:58.050 --> 06:01.050
Flying high!

06:03.730 --> 06:04.980
So, this is your chamber.

06:06.340 --> 06:08.100
It looks so...

06:09.410 --> 06:10.250
red.

06:10.930 --> 06:12.100
What's wrong?

06:12.410 --> 06:13.250
I like it.

06:14.730 --> 06:15.850
I like it too.

06:17.089 --> 06:19.048
What kind of place do you think
I should live in?

06:19.730 --> 06:21.140
I think it should be

06:21.140 --> 06:22.290
a place with flowers,

06:22.810 --> 06:24.020
cats, and dogs,

06:25.250 --> 06:26.100
bustling and lively.

06:27.930 --> 06:28.780
Aunt was injured.

06:29.100 --> 06:30.700
I couldn't have pets.

06:31.660 --> 06:32.810
This is my home.

06:33.540 --> 06:34.580
It was also Aunt's home.

06:35.290 --> 06:37.100
I'd lived with her since childhood.

06:43.340 --> 06:45.020
(Spring and Blossoms)

06:48.340 --> 06:49.780
Aunt doesn't like makeup,

06:50.170 --> 06:51.980
but to cover the bitter smell,

06:53.170 --> 06:54.580
I buy scented cakes

06:54.930 --> 06:55.780
to scent the room.

06:56.370 --> 06:57.930
This way, Aunt could always smell

06:58.220 --> 07:00.340
the four seasons of Luoying Valley.

07:01.100 --> 07:01.940
Speaking of which,

07:03.020 --> 07:04.540
I respect my father,

07:05.610 --> 07:06.730
but I admire

07:07.220 --> 07:08.220
your aunt most.

07:09.170 --> 07:10.340
As a woman,

07:11.100 --> 07:11.980
she truly controlled

07:11.980 --> 07:13.290
her life.

07:13.900 --> 07:15.930
As she wanted, she wandered Jianghu

07:16.370 --> 07:18.490
and slew the fiend.

07:19.170 --> 07:20.050
Truly

07:21.170 --> 07:22.140
free as wind and fire.

07:22.700 --> 07:24.020
Aunt told me

07:24.490 --> 07:26.050
she was satisfied with her life.

07:26.700 --> 07:28.660
Compared to the fame as a heroine,

07:29.410 --> 07:31.490
wandering

07:32.410 --> 07:34.140
with like-minded friends,

07:34.580 --> 07:35.700
doing good,

07:35.980 --> 07:36.850
sharing life and death

07:37.610 --> 07:38.690
made her freer and happier.

07:38.900 --> 07:39.810
Like

07:40.410 --> 07:41.250
Mr. Chang

07:42.020 --> 07:42.860
and Lord Qi?

07:43.170 --> 07:46.250
When Nie Hengcheng's disciples
sought revenge here,

07:46.810 --> 07:48.580
Uncle Chang and Master

07:49.020 --> 07:50.490
protected our family.

08:30.540 --> 08:34.420
(Spring and Blossoms)

08:38.530 --> 08:39.940
It's okay. Be good.

08:47.820 --> 08:49.980
You are the Nanny Chang Aunt spoke of?

08:52.220 --> 08:53.060
Yes.

08:53.250 --> 08:54.340
That's him.

09:00.370 --> 09:01.340
Later,

09:01.340 --> 09:02.420
Aunt fell ill,

09:02.420 --> 09:03.530
avoiding outsiders.

09:04.700 --> 09:06.340
Uncle Zhou's father was sick

09:06.340 --> 09:07.300
and seldom visited.

09:07.890 --> 09:09.220
Uncle Chang retired.

09:09.820 --> 09:10.660
But Master

09:11.250 --> 09:12.340
came every year.

09:12.940 --> 09:14.730
Besides Aunt and my parents,

09:14.730 --> 09:16.610
he's the one I saw most often.

09:18.370 --> 09:19.250
Lord Qi

09:20.610 --> 09:22.100
came to heal Ms. Cai?

09:24.370 --> 09:25.580
The Disintegration

09:26.010 --> 09:26.980
cut all her meridians.

09:28.130 --> 09:29.180
For decades,

09:29.730 --> 09:30.890
Master used

09:30.890 --> 09:32.220
Tianhuo Dragon Aura

09:32.220 --> 09:33.490
to sustain Aunt's life.

09:34.060 --> 09:34.900
Every year,

09:35.340 --> 09:36.490
Master stayed

09:36.490 --> 09:37.330
for a month.

09:38.010 --> 09:38.850
In that month,

09:39.130 --> 09:41.370
he expended energy every day

09:41.850 --> 09:43.060
to heal Aunt.

09:43.450 --> 09:44.756
Master's talent is extraordinary,

09:45.100 --> 09:46.770
but martial arts lag

09:47.220 --> 09:48.340
due to this.

09:48.850 --> 09:50.172
Otherwise, how could Qiu Yuanfeng

09:50.183 --> 09:52.220
act so arrogantly at the memorial?

09:55.250 --> 09:58.650
Lord Qi truly cares for Ms. Cai.

09:59.060 --> 10:00.010
Back then,

10:00.010 --> 10:02.420
he must've known Yin Dai's deeds,

10:03.250 --> 10:04.730
watching the Yin clan prosper

10:05.180 --> 10:06.580
while caring for Ms. Cai

10:07.250 --> 10:08.300
in her sickbed.

10:08.820 --> 10:09.660
It must've

10:10.820 --> 10:12.060
pained him deeply.

10:22.940 --> 10:23.780
Pingshu.

10:26.180 --> 10:27.020
I'm fine.

10:27.850 --> 10:28.890
You suffer here,

10:29.220 --> 10:30.420
yet they live freely,

10:31.340 --> 10:32.226
forgetting everything.

10:32.530 --> 10:33.370
It's fine.

10:34.820 --> 10:35.770
It doesn't matter

10:36.610 --> 10:37.650
if someone

10:38.300 --> 10:39.940
remembers.

10:40.820 --> 10:42.610
Peace of mind is more important

10:42.610 --> 10:44.340
than right or wrong.

10:45.100 --> 10:46.820
Of course, right and wrong matter.

10:46.820 --> 10:47.700
Mother said

10:47.700 --> 10:48.980
that in life,

10:48.980 --> 10:50.370
we should

10:50.370 --> 10:51.730
take revenge.

10:52.130 --> 10:53.370
Take medicine, Aunt.

10:54.610 --> 10:55.450
Sure.

11:01.980 --> 11:03.890
But the saddest thing

11:05.420 --> 11:07.580
is letting hatred cloud your mind,

11:08.890 --> 11:10.770
ruining your own life.

11:12.130 --> 11:13.220
That would only cause

11:13.890 --> 11:14.990
the ones you love to suffer

11:15.317 --> 11:16.610
and the ones you hate to rejoice.

11:21.530 --> 11:22.610
Even if Master was sad,

11:22.610 --> 11:23.610
he wouldn't say anything.

11:24.130 --> 11:25.490
He's a good man.

11:26.060 --> 11:27.890
When I was small,
swinging a silver chain,

11:27.890 --> 11:29.100
I hurt my hand.

11:29.730 --> 11:31.490
Master immediately carried me

11:31.850 --> 11:32.940
to complain to Aunt,

11:33.300 --> 11:35.300
asking why I started
martial arts so early.

11:36.010 --> 11:37.850
Aunt laughed at him for fussing,

11:38.530 --> 11:39.850
so unlike a lord.

11:40.490 --> 11:41.700
Yet after all these years,

11:41.700 --> 11:44.010
he still firmly holds his position.

11:46.700 --> 11:47.540
Enough.

11:48.300 --> 11:49.770
Your room is upstairs.

11:49.770 --> 11:50.980
Young Master, rest.

11:55.010 --> 11:56.220
If I stay upstairs,

11:58.220 --> 11:59.220
what about Song Yuzhi?

12:00.220 --> 12:01.126
He stays upstairs too.

12:27.420 --> 12:28.260
Yuzhi.

12:29.490 --> 12:30.330
Yuzhi.

12:31.220 --> 12:32.060
Father.

12:36.180 --> 12:37.130
Guangtian Sect...

12:37.650 --> 12:38.490
Guangtian Sect...

12:38.850 --> 12:40.700
Uncle Pang has contacted old members.

12:40.700 --> 12:41.700
News will come soon.

12:41.980 --> 12:43.100
Father, don't worry.

12:44.130 --> 12:44.970
Father,

12:45.340 --> 12:46.610
who attacked you

12:46.980 --> 12:48.420
and planted the Puppet Gu?

12:52.610 --> 12:53.450
Xiuzhi,

12:55.370 --> 12:57.530
why did you suddenly go to Siqi Sect

12:57.530 --> 12:58.490
the other day?

13:02.890 --> 13:03.820
Song Xiuzhi,

13:04.300 --> 13:05.650
I'm talking to you.

13:16.700 --> 13:18.060
Only a few people

13:19.130 --> 13:20.610
can hurt you with a palm.

13:21.650 --> 13:22.820
Not Zhou Zhizhen.

13:24.220 --> 13:27.420
I recognize his internal power.

13:27.850 --> 13:28.940
Could it be...

13:35.370 --> 13:36.220
Yuzhi,

13:37.820 --> 13:39.820
the Six Sects are about to change.

13:40.700 --> 13:42.700
But I'm now useless.

13:43.610 --> 13:45.060
I can't protect you.

13:45.820 --> 13:47.610
Better stay in Luoying Valley.

13:47.980 --> 13:49.530
- Zhao...
- Zhao is my junior sister.

13:51.180 --> 13:52.020
She'll only be

13:53.130 --> 13:54.530
my junior sister.

13:55.580 --> 13:57.250
The priority is to recover power.

13:57.770 --> 13:58.610
A hard battle

13:59.180 --> 14:00.530
is inevitable.

14:01.890 --> 14:02.730
Good.

14:03.300 --> 14:04.730
Since you've figured it out,

14:05.220 --> 14:06.300
I'll stop talking.

14:07.820 --> 14:09.300
After this, the world

14:10.650 --> 14:13.420
is full of opportunity.

14:16.010 --> 14:17.130
Lord Cai said

14:17.130 --> 14:18.130
I'm a guest.

14:18.130 --> 14:20.010
So, you should show me around.

14:22.300 --> 14:23.890
The braised meat shop ahead

14:24.220 --> 14:26.060
has perfected its broth
for three generations.

14:26.300 --> 14:28.166
(Braised)
Even a shoe sole smells great in it.

14:29.340 --> 14:30.490
The perfume shop

14:30.890 --> 14:32.850
(Yulan Scent)
uses the freshest flowers,

14:33.300 --> 14:35.370
steaming, drying, grinding, and mixing.

14:35.850 --> 14:37.580
My scented cakes are all from there.

14:39.130 --> 14:41.370
(Spring Tofu Pudding)
This is the Spring Tofu Pudding.

14:45.300 --> 14:46.770
You must be Uncle Douhua.

14:49.610 --> 14:50.450
Why?

14:50.770 --> 14:51.770
You know me?

14:51.770 --> 14:53.250
Zhao often mentions you.

14:53.890 --> 14:55.180
Your tofu pudding

14:55.180 --> 14:56.420
is praised endlessly.

14:58.130 --> 14:59.010
Stop talking.

14:59.010 --> 15:00.180
Try a bowl.

15:00.650 --> 15:01.580
Sure.

15:01.580 --> 15:02.420
Here, sit.

15:06.100 --> 15:07.060
Here.

15:08.100 --> 15:09.340
We were shopping.

15:09.340 --> 15:10.220
Why eat?

15:10.770 --> 15:11.610
Manager.

15:16.420 --> 15:17.260
How is it?

15:17.890 --> 15:18.890
This tofu pudding

15:19.220 --> 15:20.130
is soft yet firm

15:20.130 --> 15:21.340
and tender yet rich.

15:21.340 --> 15:22.180
Delicious!

15:22.580 --> 15:24.100
Good, eat more if you like.

15:24.530 --> 15:25.370
Manager,

15:25.370 --> 15:26.890
you eat; I'll go inside.

15:35.850 --> 15:37.220
I heard that 18 years ago,

15:37.770 --> 15:39.610
a notorious thief roamed Jiangbei.

15:40.220 --> 15:42.130
His Tai Chi was unparalleled.

15:42.820 --> 15:44.250
Later, he was captured by your aunt.

15:44.530 --> 15:45.370
Unexpectedly,

15:46.180 --> 15:47.850
using Tai Chi to grind tofu

15:49.100 --> 15:50.490
is truly ingenious.

15:54.770 --> 15:55.890
I always wondered

15:57.220 --> 15:59.580
why those outlaws your aunt knew

16:00.100 --> 16:01.580
disappeared from Jianghu.

16:03.010 --> 16:03.850
So,

16:05.100 --> 16:06.770
they were hiding in plain sight.

16:07.060 --> 16:07.900
What outlaws?

16:09.010 --> 16:11.340
They are honest businessmen.

16:12.490 --> 16:14.610
As you know, life in Jianghu isn't easy.

16:15.100 --> 16:18.010
Many heroes who were mighty in youth

16:18.370 --> 16:19.610
end up injured,

16:19.610 --> 16:20.450
ill, or old,

16:20.850 --> 16:22.300
and their later years are bleak.

16:25.650 --> 16:26.490
True.

16:27.820 --> 16:29.280
In a small place like Luoying Valley,

16:29.940 --> 16:31.940
they lived in peace for over a decade.

16:33.010 --> 16:34.650
It must have been fate.

16:35.700 --> 16:37.010
People have their destinies,

16:37.770 --> 16:39.220
but it's really about temperament.

16:39.820 --> 16:40.700
Those meant to leave

16:40.940 --> 16:42.060
will leave.

16:42.770 --> 16:43.820
Those who stay always have

16:44.980 --> 16:46.850
reasons to be held back.

16:48.100 --> 16:49.340
If they choose to remain,

16:50.130 --> 16:51.420
there's always a reason.

17:04.820 --> 17:09.420
(One stroke moves; Two strokes startle)

17:17.860 --> 17:18.700
Zhao,

17:19.330 --> 17:21.010
this place is exactly like the painting

17:21.860 --> 17:22.810
you gave me.

17:24.380 --> 17:25.290
I like it so much,

17:26.050 --> 17:27.050
and I'm very pleased.

17:28.300 --> 17:30.620
(Ingenious Study)

17:38.250 --> 17:39.420
Is this

17:40.010 --> 17:41.090
where Ms. Cai rests?

17:41.660 --> 17:42.700
Before she passed,

17:43.090 --> 17:44.250
this was her favorite place.

17:45.860 --> 17:46.980
Before she left us,

17:46.980 --> 17:48.660
she forbade us from making a fuss.

17:48.660 --> 17:49.700
So,

17:49.700 --> 17:51.860
we quietly buried her under this tree.

17:52.530 --> 17:53.370
From then on,

17:53.770 --> 17:54.900
she is free

17:55.250 --> 17:56.380
under the wind and moon.

17:57.140 --> 17:58.330
If we miss her,

17:58.330 --> 17:59.730
we'll pour some

17:59.730 --> 18:01.090
peach blossom wine here

18:01.530 --> 18:02.900
during festivals.

18:04.770 --> 18:06.010
I've dreamed of this place.

18:07.730 --> 18:09.420
This is exactly the same as in my dream.

18:09.770 --> 18:11.420
I dreamed that we ate tofu pudding,

18:12.250 --> 18:13.420
picked peach blossoms,

18:14.250 --> 18:15.090
and brewed wine.

18:15.860 --> 18:17.420
But the Luoying Valley before my eyes

18:17.810 --> 18:19.530
is much more beautiful than in my dream.

18:19.770 --> 18:20.610
Perhaps

18:21.810 --> 18:23.530
this is the place my father

18:25.220 --> 18:26.620
longed for when he was alive.

18:30.700 --> 18:32.420
If you like it,

18:33.330 --> 18:34.380
you may stay here often.

18:37.090 --> 18:37.930
Zhao,

18:39.420 --> 18:40.620
I can marry into your family.

18:45.090 --> 18:46.090
Mr. Mu,

18:47.330 --> 18:48.980
your family is prominent.

18:48.980 --> 18:50.490
Our Luoying Valley is small.

18:51.700 --> 18:53.050
I can't possibly accept that.

18:54.180 --> 18:56.250
You should think it over again.

18:56.250 --> 18:57.810
If I can't marry into your family,

18:58.700 --> 19:00.380
may my ashes be buried here?

19:01.940 --> 19:02.980
Nonsense.

19:13.050 --> 19:13.890
You failed.

19:14.250 --> 19:15.090
Watch me.

19:22.770 --> 19:24.090
You've grown up,

19:24.090 --> 19:25.570
still playing marbles like a child.

19:25.810 --> 19:26.650
Han,

19:26.940 --> 19:27.780
you lost again.

19:28.380 --> 19:29.380
What am I to you now?

19:30.570 --> 19:31.410
Brother-in-law.

19:31.700 --> 19:33.290
What? Louder.

19:33.290 --> 19:34.420
I didn't hear you.

19:34.420 --> 19:36.050
Brother-in-law!

19:38.140 --> 19:39.090
Cai Han,

19:39.380 --> 19:40.770
you sold me out for a few marbles?

19:41.050 --> 19:42.330
Han, ignore her.

19:42.900 --> 19:43.740
Let's continue.

19:44.660 --> 19:46.140
Mu Qingyan.

19:49.330 --> 19:50.380
- See? It went in.
- Yes.

19:53.330 --> 19:54.420
Marbles?

19:56.940 --> 19:57.780
Marbles!

20:09.950 --> 20:10.810
Zhao,

20:10.810 --> 20:12.530
this isn't a marble.

20:12.530 --> 20:14.290
It's fat and round,

20:14.290 --> 20:15.770
rolling around.

20:15.770 --> 20:17.660
If not a marble, what is it?

20:19.220 --> 20:20.770
Zhao is right.

20:20.770 --> 20:21.980
Fat, round,

20:21.980 --> 20:23.090
and rolling.

20:23.090 --> 20:24.220
Of course, it's a marble.

20:25.900 --> 20:27.046
What does the Jade Sunflower

20:27.180 --> 20:28.220
look like?

20:28.770 --> 20:30.530
At the Li Sect's treasury,

20:31.380 --> 20:32.490
it was burned by fire

20:33.050 --> 20:34.140
and became blackened

20:34.530 --> 20:36.980
and small.

20:38.940 --> 20:40.900
Aunt brought the Jade Sunflower back.

20:41.353 --> 20:43.399
I even played with it as a marble
when I was young.

20:46.250 --> 20:47.730
We've searched everywhere.

20:48.140 --> 20:49.940
Where could it be?

20:52.620 --> 20:54.050
Did Ms. Cai

20:54.050 --> 20:55.620
place it somewhere else?

20:56.180 --> 20:57.020
Are you saying

20:57.530 --> 20:59.050
Aunt entrusted it to someone else?

21:01.140 --> 21:02.290
Zhao!

21:03.810 --> 21:04.730
Xingjia,

21:05.900 --> 21:07.330
is everyone settled?

21:08.180 --> 21:09.020
Of course.

21:09.490 --> 21:12.010
Once I got here, I heard

21:13.090 --> 21:15.810
Mr. Mu is here to propose.

21:19.860 --> 21:21.570
He brought plenty of gold and treasures.

21:23.250 --> 21:24.090
Cai Han.

21:25.050 --> 21:25.890
Why?

21:27.900 --> 21:29.460
Enough, let's get to business.

21:29.770 --> 21:30.810
You know what happened

21:31.380 --> 21:32.570
to Guangtian Sect, right?

21:32.570 --> 21:35.050
I got a pigeon message
once I returned to the sect.

21:35.490 --> 21:37.180
Uncle Lei, worried for Yuzhi,

21:37.620 --> 21:38.620
sent me immediately.

21:44.420 --> 21:46.050
I may know where the Jade Sunflower is.

21:56.660 --> 21:57.940
Cai Pingshu,

21:58.730 --> 22:01.010
you are reckless

22:01.010 --> 22:02.490
and ignorant,

22:02.490 --> 22:04.290
leading all the women astray.

22:04.290 --> 22:06.380
Utterly foolish!

22:12.180 --> 22:13.700
I didn't say that.

22:14.010 --> 22:15.043
Abbess Jingyuan wrote it.

22:15.940 --> 22:16.810
What's that?

22:17.090 --> 22:18.420
There are worse things.

22:18.980 --> 22:19.973
Every time Aunt received

22:19.984 --> 22:21.860
Abbess Jingyuan's pigeon letter,

22:21.860 --> 22:23.180
she made me grind ink

22:23.180 --> 22:24.413
and send back scolding letters.

22:25.700 --> 22:27.090
I thought they didn't get along.

22:27.860 --> 22:28.980
Aunt was ill for years;

22:29.290 --> 22:31.380
Abbess Jingyuan never visited.

22:31.810 --> 22:32.650
Now, I see.

22:32.860 --> 22:34.380
They corresponded monthly,

22:34.559 --> 22:35.612
closer than close friends.

22:35.900 --> 22:36.770
You think

22:37.050 --> 22:38.810
Ms. Cai entrusted the Jade Sunflower

22:38.810 --> 22:39.900
to Abbess Jingyuan?

22:40.330 --> 22:42.010
After the fire,

22:42.420 --> 22:43.490
only the core remained.

22:44.050 --> 22:45.860
It could be tied to a pigeon's leg.

22:45.860 --> 22:46.700
Besides,

22:46.700 --> 22:47.700
Abbess Jingyuan

22:47.700 --> 22:50.380
openly opposed Aunt.

22:50.810 --> 22:51.900
Everyone knew.

22:52.380 --> 22:53.530
So, no one would think

22:53.940 --> 22:55.250
the Jade Sunflower

22:55.250 --> 22:56.476
was hidden at Xuankong Nunnery.

22:56.810 --> 22:57.980
Why not just check?

22:58.180 --> 22:59.020
No time to waste.

22:59.620 --> 23:00.570
Let's go quietly.

23:04.860 --> 23:06.090
The Jade Sunflower?

23:07.700 --> 23:08.660
I've never heard of it.

23:11.140 --> 23:13.050
You should reflect in Luoying Valley.

23:13.620 --> 23:15.490
Why stir trouble here?

23:16.050 --> 23:18.050
Back in Qingque Sect,

23:18.050 --> 23:19.770
how did I warn you?

23:22.050 --> 23:23.860
Why provoke the demonic sect?

23:24.980 --> 23:26.490
I didn't provoke them.

23:26.490 --> 23:27.420
You misunderstood.

23:28.330 --> 23:29.660
It wasn't Zhao provoking me;

23:31.250 --> 23:32.900
it was me provoking her.

23:33.810 --> 23:35.180
Please, don't blame Zhao.

23:35.770 --> 23:37.490
I'm weakened by the Nether Aura.

23:37.490 --> 23:38.900
My core is constrained,

23:38.900 --> 23:40.530
and I need the Sunflower to recover.

23:41.570 --> 23:42.410
Zhao is

23:43.050 --> 23:44.220
helping me.

23:44.660 --> 23:45.500
Grand-aunt,

23:45.900 --> 23:47.730
the Sunflower is too evil.

23:48.330 --> 23:51.180
It'll bring disaster
if left in the world.

23:51.620 --> 23:52.810
We want to find it

23:53.980 --> 23:54.940
and destroy it.

24:09.810 --> 24:10.660
Thank you.

24:25.770 --> 24:27.530
It really is here.

24:28.010 --> 24:28.850
Grand-aunt,

24:29.730 --> 24:32.090
didn't you say you'd never heard of it?

24:33.050 --> 24:35.180
Nuns don't lie.

24:35.530 --> 24:37.090
I didn't lie.

24:37.660 --> 24:39.730
Pingshu never called it

24:39.730 --> 24:41.090
the Jade Sunflower.

24:41.770 --> 24:42.860
I see.

24:44.050 --> 24:45.220
Aunt said nothing,

24:45.730 --> 24:47.140
yet you agreed to guard it.

24:48.140 --> 24:49.660
No wonder she entrusted it

24:50.010 --> 24:51.570
to you before dying.

24:53.570 --> 24:55.620
She said it was important.

24:55.620 --> 24:58.380
She worried someone would need it,

24:58.380 --> 25:00.050
so she didn't destroy it.

25:00.730 --> 25:01.770
She repeatedly warned me

25:02.250 --> 25:04.290
that if it was at risk of exposure,

25:04.290 --> 25:05.730
I should destroy it at once.

25:06.050 --> 25:07.050
I was careless

25:07.530 --> 25:09.380
and let it resurface.

25:10.570 --> 25:12.090
Heal here.

25:28.570 --> 25:30.290
I'm not sure if it will work.

25:30.290 --> 25:31.250
Don't worry.

25:32.250 --> 25:34.090
Pingshu used it before.

25:35.010 --> 25:36.940
How did you know

25:38.050 --> 25:39.700
the Jade Sunflower was here?

25:40.660 --> 25:41.810
The pigeon.

25:41.810 --> 25:43.010
Normally,

25:43.010 --> 25:44.256
Luoying Valley wouldn't contact

25:44.980 --> 25:46.570
those unfriendly to Aunt.

25:47.940 --> 25:49.290
Only you, Grand-aunt.

25:49.980 --> 25:51.140
Everyone knows

25:51.530 --> 25:52.730
you dislike Aunt,

25:53.570 --> 25:54.490
yet we had pigeons

25:55.090 --> 25:57.090
to Xuankong Nunnery.

25:58.490 --> 25:59.860
Xiaofeng is right.

26:00.420 --> 26:01.290
You're clever.

26:02.180 --> 26:04.660
If Pingshu were half as clever,

26:06.330 --> 26:08.290
she wouldn't have died so early.

26:16.380 --> 26:17.330
Actually,

26:18.290 --> 26:19.420
I thought

26:20.140 --> 26:21.770
you didn't like Aunt.

26:22.250 --> 26:23.900
That's true.

26:24.770 --> 26:26.900
When your mother wanted to become a nun,

26:27.290 --> 26:29.860
she caused a commotion here,

26:30.290 --> 26:31.730
forcing your mother back.

26:32.330 --> 26:34.250
I dislike her wildness,

26:35.660 --> 26:36.860
so I criticized her.

26:37.700 --> 26:38.700
Back then,

26:38.700 --> 26:40.730
Nie Hengcheng captured my disciples.

26:41.660 --> 26:43.250
Only your aunt went to save them.

26:44.050 --> 26:44.890
At that time,

26:45.220 --> 26:47.660
several of her friends died.

26:47.660 --> 26:49.700
- She just recovered.
- Slowly.

26:51.570 --> 26:53.210
- Pingshu.
- Master, save us!

26:53.330 --> 26:54.180
You're all back.

26:54.730 --> 26:56.180
Thank you, Pingshu.

26:56.620 --> 26:57.660
Take them back.

26:57.660 --> 26:58.900
Leave Nie Hengcheng to me.

26:58.900 --> 26:59.740
Alright.

27:00.940 --> 27:01.993
In less than half a month,

27:02.290 --> 27:03.620
she went to Mount Tu.

27:05.730 --> 27:08.050
You know the rest.

27:08.770 --> 27:10.420
You never went to Luoying Valley,

27:12.620 --> 27:13.860
probably to avoid

27:13.860 --> 27:15.660
seeing Aunt sick.

27:16.420 --> 27:17.770
I only wanted to remember

27:18.810 --> 27:20.860
her free-spirited self.

27:21.530 --> 27:22.730
Because of your aunt,

27:23.380 --> 27:24.620
many believe

27:24.940 --> 27:27.330
a woman can stand tall too.

27:28.420 --> 27:29.490
I recall

27:30.420 --> 27:31.420
complaining

27:32.180 --> 27:34.490
about you being too strict.

27:35.420 --> 27:37.010
Aunt said

27:37.380 --> 27:39.140
you only disliked

27:39.140 --> 27:40.980
careless behavior,

27:41.810 --> 27:45.090
but you were fair and unbiased.

27:46.010 --> 27:50.620
You two were true confidantes.

27:56.700 --> 28:01.660
(Void and Stillness)

28:06.010 --> 28:06.850
Yuzhi,

28:07.180 --> 28:08.020
how are you?

28:08.220 --> 28:09.380
The poison was cleared.

28:09.810 --> 28:11.380
With some recovery, I'll be fine.

28:13.180 --> 28:14.020
Thank you.

28:15.220 --> 28:16.250
This object is ominous.

28:16.730 --> 28:17.810
Destroy it soon.

28:18.180 --> 28:19.020
Right.

28:19.570 --> 28:21.250
It shouldn't exist in the world.

28:28.250 --> 28:29.620
Hand over the Jade Sunflower,

28:30.180 --> 28:31.570
or they die.

28:51.170 --> 28:51.950
Abbess!

28:52.050 --> 28:52.890
Abbess!

28:53.250 --> 28:54.090
Abbess!

28:54.330 --> 28:55.530
Zhao, take them first.

28:55.860 --> 28:56.730
I'll handle them.

28:56.730 --> 28:57.810
- Go.
- Go.

28:57.810 --> 28:58.650
Go.

29:18.490 --> 29:20.090
Mr. Chang's Willow Sword

29:20.090 --> 29:21.290
uses entanglement as defense.

29:22.180 --> 29:23.020
You know it,

29:23.810 --> 29:24.730
right?

29:54.660 --> 29:55.813
Hand over the Jade Sunflower,

29:56.180 --> 29:57.220
or he dies.

30:00.570 --> 30:01.410
Xingjia!

30:03.700 --> 30:04.540
Hand it over.

30:07.530 --> 30:08.370
Switch.

30:16.090 --> 30:17.010
Xingjia,

30:17.010 --> 30:17.850
are you okay?

30:18.010 --> 30:18.860
I'm fine.

30:18.860 --> 30:19.700
I won't die.

30:20.050 --> 30:20.940
The Jade Sunflower!

30:21.250 --> 30:22.090
Chase him!

30:22.330 --> 30:23.170
It's fine.

30:23.450 --> 30:24.420
The Night Orchid is gone.

30:24.420 --> 30:25.703
The Jade Sunflower is of no use.

30:27.860 --> 30:28.730
What do you mean?

30:29.940 --> 30:31.380
They need both the Jade Sunflower

30:31.380 --> 30:33.436
and the Night Orchid to practice.

30:33.450 --> 30:34.370
Without both, it fails.

30:34.370 --> 30:35.230
But

30:35.980 --> 30:36.980
I have the Night Orchid.

30:37.250 --> 30:38.090
What?

30:38.290 --> 30:39.660
It's not that.

30:39.660 --> 30:40.940
I have a little left.

30:40.940 --> 30:41.980
I gave it to Uncle...

30:41.980 --> 30:42.820
They're here.

30:43.660 --> 30:44.500
They're here!

30:50.290 --> 30:51.130
Yuzhi,

30:51.380 --> 30:53.290
leave with the Abbess and Xingjia.

30:53.290 --> 30:54.130
I'll cover.

30:54.540 --> 30:55.380
You go.

30:55.380 --> 30:56.490
Xingjia is badly injured.

30:56.490 --> 30:57.620
I can't carry him.

30:57.620 --> 30:58.460
Go.

30:59.980 --> 31:00.940
Zhao...

31:00.940 --> 31:02.050
Don't worry, Abbess.

31:02.700 --> 31:04.010
I was raised by my aunt.

31:22.620 --> 31:23.460
Cai Zhao!

31:24.140 --> 31:25.330
You demoness!

31:26.810 --> 31:28.900
You repeatedly ruined my plans.

31:29.220 --> 31:31.140
Today, you're mine.

31:35.140 --> 31:36.330
Seize her for me!

31:46.900 --> 31:48.570
The Ziwei Method is powerful.

32:06.570 --> 32:07.410
Stop chasing.

32:35.660 --> 32:36.530
Mu Qingyan.

32:38.180 --> 32:39.020
Go!

32:39.250 --> 32:40.090
Chase!

32:47.090 --> 32:49.050
Mu Qingyan, get down here!

32:49.050 --> 32:50.730
You coward!

32:50.730 --> 32:51.620
Mr. Yu.

33:04.010 --> 33:04.850
You didn't die.

33:05.330 --> 33:06.180
Surprised?

33:09.810 --> 33:10.860
What a relief.

33:13.570 --> 33:15.700
Do you know how much I missed you

33:16.140 --> 33:18.140
and how much I regret what I did?

33:20.380 --> 33:22.140
Fengge, forgive me.

33:22.140 --> 33:23.530
Do you really regret it?

33:24.050 --> 33:25.330
Yes.

33:33.090 --> 33:34.010
Fengge,

33:34.900 --> 33:36.530
you're back now.

33:46.380 --> 33:47.330
Why?

33:57.700 --> 33:58.570
We

34:00.050 --> 34:01.180
are even.

34:13.260 --> 34:14.100
Zhao!

34:15.740 --> 34:16.580
Zhao!

34:18.740 --> 34:19.580
Zhao!

34:34.440 --> 34:35.300
Young Master,

34:35.300 --> 34:37.650
stop sending inner power to Miss Cai,

34:37.650 --> 34:39.650
or you'll die.

34:46.980 --> 34:47.820
Young Master,

34:47.820 --> 34:48.660
this...

34:50.380 --> 34:51.530
If she dies,

34:53.090 --> 34:54.530
what do you think I'll do?

35:07.010 --> 35:07.850
Zhao,

35:10.610 --> 35:12.130
it will soon be over.

35:44.980 --> 35:45.820
Zhao.

35:46.300 --> 35:47.140
Zhao?

35:53.340 --> 35:54.570
You've slept for days.

35:55.530 --> 35:56.650
If I hadn't come,

35:58.530 --> 35:59.570
you would be dead.

36:09.740 --> 36:11.340
That man in black is strong.

36:12.490 --> 36:13.740
How did you escape?

36:14.610 --> 36:15.690
I have my ways.

36:18.170 --> 36:19.010
Here.

36:19.610 --> 36:20.450
Take medicine.

36:39.170 --> 36:40.300
Smiley.

36:41.130 --> 36:42.050
Not as good as yours.

36:42.860 --> 36:43.740
Just make do.

36:57.490 --> 36:58.330
Zhao,

37:01.050 --> 37:02.980
the man in black

37:05.090 --> 37:06.300
feels like someone I know.

37:11.041 --> 37:21.701
=Generation to Generation=

37:40.461 --> 37:44.871
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:45.436 --> 37:50.051
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:50.391 --> 37:54.956
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

37:55.481 --> 37:59.781
♪Free to wander in the world♪

38:02.726 --> 38:07.426
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:07.951 --> 38:12.241
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:12.901 --> 38:16.931
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:17.246 --> 38:22.371
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:22.946 --> 38:27.756
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:27.971 --> 38:32.141
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:32.866 --> 38:36.801
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:37.301 --> 38:42.576
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

39:05.306 --> 39:10.436
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:10.801 --> 39:15.171
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:15.436 --> 39:19.566
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:19.751 --> 39:25.326
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
